---
/**
 * CTAFinal — bandeau full-width sombre, citation finale + bouton cuivre.
 */
---

<section class="relative bg-salon-encre text-salon-creme py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-10 text-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Halo cuivre subtle en arrière-plan -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] rounded-full"
         style="background: radial-gradient(50% 50% at 50% 50%, rgb(181 105 77 / 0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <p class="scroll-reveal flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-salon-laiton">
      <span class="inline-block w-8 h-px bg-salon-laiton" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span>Maison Aurore</span>
      <span class="inline-block w-8 h-px bg-salon-laiton" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </p>

    <h2 class="scroll-reveal mt-6 font-playfair font-bold text-salon-creme leading-[1.1]" style="font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);">
      Envie de
      <span class="italic font-medium text-salon-cuivre">changer de coupe ?</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="scroll-reveal mt-6 text-salon-creme/75 leading-relaxed">
      Prenez rendez-vous, on s'occupe du reste. Diagnostic offert, conseils sans pression, résultat à votre image.
    </p>

    <div class="scroll-reveal mt-10">
      <a
        href="#rendez-vous"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-14 px-9 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] rounded-full bg-salon-cuivre text-salon-blanc hover:bg-[#7C3F2A] transition-all"
        style="box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgb(181 105 77 / 0.45);"
      >
        Prendre rendez-vous
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
